---
// src/components/HouseRebuild.astro
---
 
<!-- Back link -->
<div class="section-dark pt-28 sm:pt-32 pb-0 px-5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <a href="/community" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-body text-amber-400/70 text-sm hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors duration-200 mb-8">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18"/>
      </svg>
      Back to Community
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
 
<!-- Story hero -->
<div class="section-dark pb-16 px-5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-400/10 border border-amber-400/20 font-body text-amber-400 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
      House Rebuild · 2025
    </span>
    <h1 class="section-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white leading-tight mb-8">
      A Family Lost Everything.<br/>
      <span class="text-amber-400">eKoneni Built It Back.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      Fire doesn't ask permission. It came at night, and by morning a mother and her children
      had nothing left — no walls, no roof, no belongings. eKoneni didn't wait to be called.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
<!-- Cover image -->
<div class="section-dark pb-0 px-5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[320px] sm:min-h-[440px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10 mb-3">
      <!-- Swap for real image when ready:
      <img src="/images/community/house-rebuild-cover.jpg" alt="eKoneni rebuilds a family home" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
      -->
      <div class="text-center p-8">
        <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-amber-400/20 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="font-body text-amber-400/30 text-sm">Replace with cover photo</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-xs text-center mb-16">eKoneni Lounge · Mdantsane, 2025</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
<!-- Story body -->
<section class="section-mid py-16 px-5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
 
    <!-- Narrative -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
      <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        The fire broke out last week. By the time it was out, the house was stripped bare — roof gone,
        walls charred, everything the family owned reduced to ash. A mother. Her children. Nowhere to go.
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Word reached eKoneni. And that was enough. Within days, the team arrived with materials, paint,
        and the kind of energy that doesn't wait for a committee meeting. They got to work.
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Roofing — done. Painting — done. The walls that once stood are standing again.
        The work isn't finished. Electrical fitting is the next step, and eKoneni won't stop
        until that house has power and that family is fully, truly home.
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        No press conference. No sponsorship deal. Just people from Mdantsane,
        looking after Mdantsane. <span class="text-amber-200/80">Masihlangane — let us come together.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Progress timeline -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="section-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white mb-8">
        The <span class="text-amber-400">Progress</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-white font-medium">Roofing completed</p>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm">The structure is sealed. The family has shelter again.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-white font-medium">Painting completed</p>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm">Fresh walls. A home starting to look like a home again.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-400/15 border border-amber-400/30 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-amber-300 font-medium">Electrical fitting — in progress</p>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm">The final step. When this is done, the family has power and a fully restored home.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Photo grid -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="section-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white mb-8">
        On the <span class="text-amber-400">Ground</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[220px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10">
          <!-- <img src="/images/community/house-rebuild-before.jpg" alt="Before the rebuild" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> -->
          <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">Before photo</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[220px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10">
          <!-- <img src="/images/community/house-rebuild-after.jpg" alt="After the rebuild" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> -->
          <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">After photo</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[220px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10">
          <!-- <img src="/images/community/house-rebuild-team.jpg" alt="eKoneni team working" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> -->
          <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">The team at work</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[220px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10">
          <!-- <img src="/images/community/house-rebuild-family.jpg" alt="The family" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> -->
          <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">The family</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Video section -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="section-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white mb-8">
        Watch the <span class="text-amber-400">Story</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 border border-amber-400/10 min-h-[280px] sm:min-h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
        <!--
          Facebook embed:
          <iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=YOUR_VIDEO_URL"
            class="w-full min-h-[400px]" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
 
          YouTube embed:
          <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YOUR_VIDEO_ID"
            class="w-full min-h-[400px]" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        -->
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-amber-400/20 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.91 11.672a.375.375 0 010 .656l-5.603 3.113a.375.375 0 01-.557-.328V8.887c0-.286.307-.466.557-.327l5.603 3.112z"/>
          </svg>
          <p class="font-body text-amber-400/40 text-sm mb-1">Video coming soon</p>
          <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">Replace with Facebook or YouTube embed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Quote -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-400/10 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400/5 to-transparent p-8 sm:p-10 mb-16">
      <p class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-amber-400/80 italic leading-relaxed mb-4">
        "The same Mdantsane that fills our dancefloor is the Mdantsane we go home to. We don't forget that."
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-sm">— eKoneni Lounge</p>
    </div>
 
    <!-- Nav footer -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 pt-8 border-t border-amber-400/10">
      <a href="/community" class="btn-outline px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-body text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18"/>
        </svg>
        All Stories
      </a>
      <a href="/community/feeding-scheme" class="font-body text-amber-400 text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-3 transition-all duration-200">
        Next: Two Weeks. Every Child Fed.
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
 
  </div>
</section>
